    "patch_code": "private boolean checkStartWithSlashAsteriskStarOrEndingStar(String s) {\n  int len = s.length();\n  return s.charAt(len - 1) == '/' && ((len > 3 && s.charAt(len - 3) == '*') ||\n      (len >= 3 && s.substring(0, 3).equals(\"/**\")));\n}\n  \nprivate boolean startsWithBang(String value) {\n  int i = 0;\n  while (true) {\n    char ch = value.charAt(i++);\n    if (ch != '!') {\n      continue;\n    }\n    return true;\n  }\n}\n\nprivate void handleBlockComment(Comment comment) {\n  String value = comment.getValue();\n  // Check for preserved license headers, preserving trailing whitespace.\n  if (startsWithBang(value)) {\n    System.out.println(\"/*\" + value.trim() + \"*/\");\n    return;\n  }\n  if (!checkStartWithSlashAsteriskStarOrEndingStar(value)) {\n    errorReporter.warning(\n        SUSPICIOUS_COMMENT_WARNING,\n        sourceName,\n        comment.getLineno(), \"\", 0);\n  }\n}",
